<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Patrick KT Lai on Connectome</title><link>https://connectome.tw/authors/patrick-kt-lai/</link><description>Recent content in Patrick KT Lai on Connectome</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-tw</language><copyright>© 2026</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 25 May 2014 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://connectome.tw/authors/patrick-kt-lai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Biosimilar─past and future (Part II)</title><link>https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-part-ii/</link><pubDate>Sun, 25 May 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-part-ii/</guid><description>繼上回分析 Biosimilar 對傳統小分子藥物其實並未十分有衝擊後 (&lt;a href="https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-1/" >Biosimilar - past and future Part I&lt;/a>，Patrick 進一步敘述目前市場上 Biosimilar 的發展情形，且讓我們一起來瞭解。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-part-ii/feature.jpg"/></item><item><title>裘莉與阿湯哥的聖戰─從基因檢測到預防性手術及犯罪預防</title><link>https://connectome.tw/posts/genetic-test/</link><pubDate>Sun, 13 Apr 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://connectome.tw/posts/genetic-test/</guid><description>去年全球熱門頭條 –「安潔莉納裘莉切除雙邊乳房」，相信大家還記憶猶新。她為求能陪伴孩子們多些時光而選擇動手術的舉動，贏得媒體大眾的一片讚賞。這舉動對於好萊塢首席女星的演藝生崖衝擊之大可想而知，但在一片美譽背後，媒體和評論家都忽略了未來人類健康照護的可能隱憂，其中牽涉到人權自由意志和政府監控等議題。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://connectome.tw/posts/genetic-test/feature.jpg"/></item><item><title>Biosimilar─past and future (Part I)</title><link>https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-1/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-1/</guid><description>發展 Biosimilar 為近年藥物開發的主題之一，然而 Biosimilar 的引入是否會對傳統小分子藥物帶來甚大衝擊？且讓我們藉 Patrick 的文章分析一窺究竟。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://connectome.tw/posts/biosimilar-past-and-future-1/feature.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>